# 🚆 Product Sales of Train – Data Analysis Dashboard

![Dashboard Preview](train%20data%20.png)

> **📊 Project Overview**
> This dashboard provides an interactive analysis of **Train Product Sales**, helping users understand sales performance across different **cities, regions, products, customers, and shipping modes**. It enables business managers to monitor sales trends, identify high-performing products, and make data-driven decisions using Excel Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, and Slicers.

---

# 🎯 Objectives

* 📈 Analyze total sales performance.
* 🌍 Compare sales across different regions and cities.
* 🚂 Identify the best-selling train products.
* 🚚 Evaluate shipping mode performance.
* 👥 Monitor customer purchasing behavior.
* 📊 Create an interactive dashboard for business insights.

