# 🚀 Business Recommendations

* 📢 Promote low-selling products through discounts or bundled offers.
* 🎯 Focus marketing campaigns on high-performing regions and cities.
* 🤝 Build loyalty programs for repeat and high-value customers.
* 🚚 Continue optimizing **Standard Class** shipping while evaluating opportunities to increase adoption of premium shipping options.
* 📦 Monitor inventory based on top-selling products to avoid stock shortages.

